--- State expected throughput direction, loss/reward risk, baseline requirement, and user confirmation gate.
--- Keep all evidence path-only. Never paste raw logs, full tracebacks, credentials, private IPs, profiling dumps, full diffs, install logs, or real NPU artifacts into main context.
--- Do not edit optimization code.
--- Do not create or start containers.
--- Do not run baseline or optimized training.
--- Do not claim performance improvement.
